token_info.name: GENÓMICA 1
token_info.description: This interactive NFT is the world’s first virtual ecosystem of micro species created using machine learning and AI  — a concept of ambient ‘Living Art’.  Each species in this artwork is unique and has never been seen before. During the AI process just a few are captured before they disappear forever. The unique sounds of the animals were created using modular audio synthesis.  Click on the species to see them move. Press the logo for more info and Audio On/Off. Full screen option bottom right.
